<section class="section-54">
    <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-72 w-container">
        <h1 class="heading-64">Work With Wolfe</h1>
        <div class="text-block-197">At Wolfe, we&#x27;re the KPI free recruitment agency. We&#x27;re the mavericks, the trailblazers, the ones who dare to challenge the status quo. We&#x27;re not here to fit into the corporate mold; we&#x27;re here to break it. Welcome to a world where recruitment isn&#x27;t just about filling roles; it&#x27;s about building a vibrant community of diverse minds and spirited individuals.</div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="section-56">
    <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-74 w-container">
        <div class="div-block-195">
            <div class="div-block-197">
                <h1 class="heading-61">Perth &amp; Sydney Offices</h1>
                <div>With our Sydney office now in full swing, we&#x27;re not just expanding our physical presence; we&#x27;re expanding the horizons of what recruitment can be. Wolfe remains the go-to agency for the recruiters who dare to be different, who thrive on community, and who are ready to make their mark in a world that needs authenticity above all.<br /><br />So, whether you&#x27;re in Sydney or Perth, welcome to Wolfe, we think you&#x27;re going to like it here.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="div-block-196"><img src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/624a9b9e190a932a33ecd42f/64e6b79d6e6ad43bbf857d91_wolfstralia.png" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 36vw, (max-width: 991px) 37vw, (max-width: 1439px) 31vw, (max-width: 6250px) 32vw, 2000px" srcset="https://assets-global.website-files.com/624a9b9e190a932a33ecd42f/64e6b79d6e6ad43bbf857d91_wolfstralia-p-500.png 500w, https://assets-global.website-files.com/624a9b9e190a932a33ecd42f/64e6b79d6e6ad43bbf857d91_wolfstralia-p-800.png 800w, https://assets-global.website-files.com/624a9b9e190a932a33ecd42f/64e6b79d6e6ad43bbf857d91_wolfstralia-p-1080.png 1080w, https://assets-global.website-files.com/624a9b9e190a932a33ecd42f/64e6b79d6e6ad43bbf857d91_wolfstralia-p-1600.png 1600w, https://assets-global.website-files.com/624a9b9e190a932a33ecd42f/64e6b79d6e6ad43bbf857d91_wolfstralia.png 2000w" alt="" class="image-41" /></div>
